Package assignment

Provides classes for assignments.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Assignment
    An Assignment has a category, a collection of submissions and a collection of assignment grades.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AssignmentCategory
    An AssignmentCategory contains an AssignmentCategory parent to which it belongs, a collection of AssignmentCategory to be subcategories, and a collection of Assignments that are a part of AsignemntCategory.
    AssignmentGrade
    An AssignmentGrade contains an Assignment for which the grade is associated with, an integer, rawScore, which is the points assignment has earned, and a LetterGrade which represents the letter grade the assignment has earned.
    AssignmentSubmission
    An AssignemntSubmission contains an Assignment representing the specific assignment to be submitted, and a Date representing the date and time of the submission.
